name: Cybrog Girl : Cyan the Ice Cold
description:
Cyan is one of the 4 special cybrog girls, along with Magenta, Yellow and Black.

 Cyan the coldest cybrog girl representing her element, "The ICE". Her serious attitude makes very difficult to impress her with anything. But, behind her cold nature, she has a very kind and caring heart, only, it's still difficult for this cybrog to express it.
